&lt;p>&lt;a href="https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/90104614" target="_blank" rel="noopener">用 pbds 过 luogu P3369【模板】普通平衡树&lt;/a>&lt;/p></description></item><item><title>Finding the longest path on a DAG</title><link>https://tgc54.com/post/longestpathondag/</link><pubDate>Wed, 19 Feb 2020 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://tgc54.com/post/longestpathondag/</guid><description>&lt;div class="highlight">&lt;pre tabindex="0" class="chroma">&lt;code class="language-cpp" data-lang="cpp">&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="n">vector&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">&amp;lt;&lt;/span>&lt;span class="kt">int&lt;/span>&lt;span class="o">&amp;gt;&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">G&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">[&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">N&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">];&lt;/span>
&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;span class="line">&lt;span class="cl">&lt;span class="kt">int&lt;/span> &lt;span class="n">dp&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">[&lt;/span>&lt;span class="n">N&lt;/span>&lt;span class="p">];&lt;/span>
